sql_query.sql:
SELECT lower(name) FROM "groups" WHERE (messageable_level in (99) OR
          (
            messageable_level = 3 AND id in (
            SELECT group_id FROM group_users WHERE user_id = 3)
          ) OR (
            messageable_level = 4 AND id in (
            SELECT group_id FROM group_users WHERE user_id = 3 AND owner IS TRUE)
          )) AND (lower(name) in (NULL))
